text: Zsombor Garát (born July 27, 1997) is a Hungarian professional ice hockey Defenceman who currently plays for Cedar Rapids RoughRiders in the United States Hockey League. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Cedar Rapids RoughRiders players Category:Living people Category:Hungarian ice hockey defencemen Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
